data.text:
EPISODE 1

Tommy's First Birthday

It's Tommy's first ever birthday, and his parents have planned a huge party for him and his pals. Meanwhile, Tommy is convinced that eating dog food will turn him into a dog.

21 min Â· 10 Aug 1991 G

EPISODE 2

Barbeque / Waiter, There's a Baby in My Soup

Tommy loses his ball in the neighbour's back garden when Angelica hits it over the fence, and he goes on a mission to try to get it back. Then, Tommy runs wild in a chic restaurant that he's visiting with his parents.

21 min Â· 17 Aug 1991 G

EPISODE 3

At the Movies / Slumber Party

Tommy and the Rugrats wander around a cinema, leaving a path of destruction behind them. Then, Tommy gets a cold when Angelica comes to stay at his house and keeps the windows open.

20 min Â· 24 Aug 1991 G

EPISODE 4

Baby Commercial / Little Dude

Phil and Lil cause chaos as the stars of a baby diaper advertisement. Then, Didi brings Tommy to the school where she teaches, for use as a visual aid in Home Economics. He becomes the coolest baby in class.

22 min Â· 7 Sept 1991 G

EPISODE 5

Beauty Contest / Baseball

Grandpa and Stu dress Tommy as a girl in the hope of winning a beauty pageant contest that would see them taking home a boat as a prize. Then, Grandpa takes Tommy to a baseball game, and Tommy explores the stadium.

21 min Â· 14 Sept 1991 G
